locations: Wettingen, Kanton Aargau, Switzerland::(exteriors and interiors Switzerland)
imdb.plot outline: The «Spalenbühl» is perhaps the coolest school anywhere in Switzerland. There is always something going on at the «Spali» because «Best Friends» Fiona, Irmak, Lukas, Flip, Tobi (Juniors), as well as seniors Avalanche, Beni, Jula, Lena and Marko are up to so many different things. Indeed, they are as varied as their pursuits. Twins with the principal as their dad; a guy from Montenegro who wants to be a journalist someday; a freaky girl who designs all her own clothes; the son of a Swiss chicken farmer - and many more. They all have their problems. But with a little help from their friends - Best Friends - they get by just fine.
